    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per the ASME V&V 40 framework. The CFD model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 at all evaluated operating points satisfies the COU acceptance criterion.",
